If this was implimented, would wizards really get all cranky and upset? Baring in mind that these pets are manna dependant and CAN run out!<br><br>And, on a final note, let's keep the maturity level higher than the Jerry Springer show, please! <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#33333><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/ujarnin.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Jarnin</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Sorcerer</span><br> <font color=#ffffff>(8/3/02 9:52:55 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm10.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=745.topic&index=1>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://www.interofficenetworks.com/demo/doh/neriakwraith.jpg WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Magician Fire Pets: Imbicilic Wizards</span><hr size=1> I can officially say that I could give a rats ass if a magicians level 52+ fire pet casted enticement of flames. <p><CENTER><EMBED src="http://www.interofficenetworks.com/demo/doh/barcode.swf" quality=high bgcolor=#000000  WIDTH="220" HEIGHT="60" NAME="barcode" ALIGN="" TYPE="application/x-shockwave-flash" PLUGINSPAGE="http://www.macromedia.com/go/getflashplayer"></EMBED></CENTER></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#000000><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/urochenko.showPublicProfile?language=EN>rochenko</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Wizard</span><br> <font color=#ffffff>(8/5/02 8:30:09 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm10.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=745.topic&index=2>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Magician Fire Pets: Imbicilic Wizards</span><hr size=1> more power to 'em.  It's a mana pig that does low dmg, but I actually think it's a great Idea to help mages out on raids.  I'm all for it.<br><br>Hrav